"{\"description\":\"Senior Technical Officer [Track] - Cardiff (Canton). Provide technical support to the Maintenance Engineering team. Key responsibilities include carrying out work safely, quality management, technical support and guidance, equipment design and installation, inspections and investigations, work prioritization, materials specification, calibration and certification of tools, and database management. Required competencies include technical knowledge, safety promotion, effective communication, coaching and development, relevant qualifications, and willingness to drive vehicles.\",\"howToApply\":\"To apply for this position, click 'apply now' and follow the instructions on the application portal. The closing date for applications is 1st December 2023. Late applications will not be accepted. Please note that prospective candidates will be required to undergo and pass a drugs and alcohol test as part of the pre-employment checks.\",\"aboutTheRole\":{\"essential\":[\"Carrying out work safely\",\"Quality management\",\"Technical support and guidance\",\"Equipment design and installation\",\"Inspections and investigations\",\"Work prioritization\",\"Materials specification\",\"Calibration and certification of tools\",\"Database management\"],\"desirable\":[],\"keyAccountabilities\":[\"Carry out work safely\",\"Adhere to company policies and procedures\",\"Manage and check the quality of work delivered and confirm assets are compliant to standards\",\"Manage the preparation of work and resource specifications, method statements and plans\",\"Provide technical support and guidance\",\"Design, install, test and commission equipment\",\"Undertake and supervise technical tasks, survey and design work\",\"Undertake technical inspections, tests, investigations and analysis of technical data\",\"Prioritise work arising and agree work plans for the group\",\"Prepare specifications and requisition for materials\",\"Manage processes and systems for the calibration and certification of tools and equipment\",\"Manage information to update systems, databases and records\",\"Contribute to your own development and that of others\"]}}"